Project : smart_irrigation_mesh
Author  : swordenkisk | github.com/swordenkisk/smart_irrigation_mesh
Created : March 2026
Source  : ideas_database.db — idea score 89.0/100

Domain      : AgriTech
Technology  : IoT + LoRaWAN + Federated Learning + ML Forecasting
Problem     : Agriculture consumes 70% of global fresh water; most is wasted.
Solution    : Self-organising mesh of soil sensors + Penman-Monteith ET₀ + FedAvg
Impact      : 40–55% water reduction — billions of m³ saved annually

Novelty: 97/100 | Feasibility: 79/100 | Impact: 97/100

Physics core : FAO-56 Penman-Monteith ET₀ + Bucket soil moisture model
ML core      : FedAvg federated learning (privacy-preserving, no raw data sharing)
Standards    : LoRaWAN, MQTT, FAO-56
